::Feline::

She looked at the console as HotRod's memory finished downloading.  
She smiled evilly and looked up at Zardus.  "I have it.  I have the 
codes to the security systems and autoweapons from him.  I have the 
scematics and blue prints to the Cybertron Fire. Shall I print it all 
out for you Zardus?"

She looked up at HotRod and smiled,"Would you like to program him to 
be loyal to you Zardus?"
